THANK YOU" + a card-name fragment is decisive.
{% elif fixme_root == "Equity" %}This is an EQUITY FIXME — usually an
owner draw, owner contribution, or opening/closing balance reset.
Pick the equity account aligned with the entity that owns this
movement. These are rare and usually deliberate; low-confidence
classifications should defer to a human.
{% elif fixme_root == "Assets" %}This is an ASSETS FIXME — typically
the destination side of an inter-account transfer. Pick the
account (savings, secondary checking, brokerage, etc.) that
received these funds given the narration. Source-side information
lives in the other posting and the card binding.
