Return:
- target_account: MUST be copied verbatim from the whitelist above.
- confidence: 0.0 to 1.0. Use >= 0.95 only when the merchant and
  history leave essentially no doubt.
- reasoning: one sentence, plain English.
- intercompany_flag: set TRUE ONLY when you selected an account
  whose entity differs from the card-binding entity above — i.e.,
  this is a wrong-card situation that needs a four-leg correction.
  Leave FALSE whenever target_account's entity equals the
  card-binding entity.
- owning_entity: when intercompany_flag=TRUE, set this to the
  target_account's entity (the entity that actually incurred the
  expense). Else null.
